  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add olive oil and a pinch of red pepper flakes to the heated pan.",
    "Toss in sliced chives and pickle for about 1 minute until they start to wilt slightly.",
    "Fold in dates, ensuring to mix evenly with the ingredients. Sprinkle kalamansi juice and soy sauce on top.",
    "Stir-fry everything together for another 2-3 minutes or until you achieve your desired gooey texture.",
    "Remove from heat immediately after serving."
